    "• Performance Metrics: The performance of each model was evaluated using the following metrics: accuracy, F1 score, confusion matrix, precision, and recall.",
    "The models were first evaluated on the training dataset to assess their training performance and, then, on a separate test dataset to assess their generalization performance.",
    "• Hardware and Software: All experiments were conducted on a machine with an Intel Core i7 CPU, 32 GB of RAM, and an NVIDIA Tesla P100 Data Center GPU.",
    "The models were implemented using Python 3.9 and the TensorFlow 2.4 deep learning library.",
    "• Comparison: The performance of each model was compared based on their accuracy, F1 score, and the number of total, trainable, and non-trainable parameters as well as precision, recall, and weighted average."
